race.description: The Brothers Leagues Club Open Handicap
race.comment: Competitive with several on the quick back-up from the same race eight days ago behind Northern Pride. One of those was TYCOON BEAU (4) who kept coming and finished a close-up third. Drawn for a good run and expected to go close again. OBLIGATED (3) was a close-up third fresh and is a second-up winner. Has good stats for this and appeals as the main threat. SWEET KISSES (5) is another doing the quick turnaround and finished just behind TYCOON BEAU. Gave a sight in that race and drawn to do the same. FROM THIS MOMENT (9) is yet another from that race and finished fourth. Races on speed and will give a sight again. INCHING CLOSER (6) is a veteran who is much better than the last couple. Has a strong record this trip and can improve.
